contributionDescription: I am here to support by means of delegation and participating in community activities. I will also buy a lot of Optimism in the future and will participate in voting governance. For me, Optimism is a fast, stable, and scalable L2 solution built on Ethereum.
impactDescription:
The ecosystem is small but they have some great projects on there.
I am  confident their tech stack and the attention Base will bring is going to bring a lot of projects over. I am optimistic we'll see a few. Cheers Optimistic people and to the developers!
pwFlaggedReason: This application should be flagged for promising future impact and contributions, which is against the rules of the grant program.
